{"tid":1648270,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[建議]文宣制圖方程式:激起情緒->引導->行動呼籲","createTime":"2019-10-12T06:31:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T10:35:05.000Z","uid":50904,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"634253626d233c801e577b110961d1899218d4df","tid":1648270,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:31:29.000Z","msg":"依加文宣有好多設計人幫手整到好靚，如果背後嘅目標受眾、理念、同目標再針對性啲就可有更大效果。因為文宣唔係純粹為左令文字變圖、亦唔係純粹提供資訊，而係一種marketing<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過公道啲講，好多時活動發起人、比idea想有人出圖嘅人本身都未必有諗清楚，其實又唔可以怪文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得去到最簡化黎講文宣應該要有三樣野:<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>激起情緒-&gt;引導-&gt;行動呼籲</strong></span><br />\n例如下面呢位義士嘅相<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JQXzVR5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJQXzVR5.jpg&h=11559325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-&gt;<span style=\"color: orange;\">情緒</span>:傷心/感動/內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-&gt;<span style=\"color: orange;\">引導</span>:你應該要以罷工黎支持前線手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-&gt;<span style=\"color: orange;\">行動</span>:參與罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家經常整好多關於警暴嘅文宣，但係無引導讀者嘅情緒、更加無提供對抗/解決嘅行動，結果其實係反而幫手令黑警嘅武力震懾更成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CauOf9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCauOf9e.jpg&h=843ad285&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n好似我屋企人咁，佢每次睇完到大家傳啲黑警嘅片嘅反應係:<br />\n-&gt;<span style=\"color: orange;\">情緒</span>:嬲、啲差佬無人性架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-&gt;<span style=\"color: orange;\">自然反應</span>:怕、所以你千期唔好參加呢啲遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-&gt;<span style=\"color: orange;\">行動</span>:唔好參加、唔好硬碰、心中支持但身體很實誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n大家不妨參考下1/2次世界大戰嘅propaganda art，佢地係用好多心理學嘅方式挑起你嘅情緒、好有指向性，直頭好似同你1對1對話咁。<br />\n例如下邊我將佢同啲現有文宣圖mix埋個感覺已經好唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呼籲全民抗爭</span></strong></div></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWVUVZF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWVUVZF.png&h=347039f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>建立黃色經濟圈</strong></div></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5P8O0sL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5P8O0sL.jpg&h=fb3bae29&s={SIZE}\" />    <br />\nbtw,叫人down app如果加埋QR code更好，你睇大公報連寫勒索信都會教人點買bitcoin<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人反抗/打狗救人</span></strong></div></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QpZyses.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQpZyses.jpg&h=2f3850af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依加最少係呢種關於反抗精神/加入街頭抗爭/黑警唔係無敵嘅文宣<br />\n其實想搵之前前線手足打到黑警一仆一碌段片cap圖出黎，可惜記得咩keyword<br />\n但岳義精神應該都唔算離題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"961e2e3cfc5aae640bf57fd63405e04a3b683c16","tid":1648270,"uid":50904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:32:02.000Z","msg":"Propaganda中文叫政治宣傳，因為呢樣野做得最成功嘅係二戰嘅德國，<br />\n所以Propaganda呢個字通常帶有洗腦/思想操縱等等嘅負面評價，但我引用返下邊youtube片嘅講法:<br />\n&quot;...propaganda as a tool is no more moral or immoral than a pump handle.&quot; - Harold Lasswell<br />\nMorality enters the picture when one judges the ends for which propaganda is used<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Introduction to Propaganda</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-WpFzTplp28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-WpFzTplp28&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKPjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=11242f01\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-WpFzTplp28</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Propaganda During World War 1</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3t_Gwo3M-uc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3t_Gwo3M-uc&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKPjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=ef58f793\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3t_Gwo3M-uc</a><br />\n<br />\n順便再推一次自己嘅舊post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>[終極攻略]點樣做會贏? 一齊學習戰爭同戰略</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1599005/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1599005/</a>"},{"pid":"5c76768c023870ab3e938be90b42b02fdd4a25dd","tid":1648270,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:34:10.000Z","msg":"推多3次就讓路比3點大遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f413f8e7bd81225fc072887edfd7b3637d43cdd","tid":1648270,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a611c5d173e1f6703fa7459793cf9b07f8eb26f2","tid":1648270,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8edf8cd0f8cdaaa89f351f8c0e4a6596ba2efa","tid":1648270,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"